channel.title: [Delta] Very strange problem
channel.description:
So this has never been a problem for me before, maybe I just forgot how to do it since I haven't done it in along time.
Okay the problem is I am adding models in..I put the .dat file in my models folder, I go to class.8 and add my ints.
Switch over to my source put the item id in the item.cfg...go to item.java and put the appropriate equipping.
Well when I do my pickup command and get the item..it shows up invisible and its invisible as I equip it..it shows the name when I right click it and etc..it is not the model because I have tried other ones to...
What have I done wrong?
